<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Descubra a Suíça 🇨🇭</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;700&family=Open+Sans:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
:root {
    --suica-vermelho: #d52b1e;
    --suica-escuro: #2d3436;
    --gelo: #f1f2f6;
}

* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
    background: var(--gelo);
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    color: #333;
}

/* HERO */
.hero {
    height: 100vh;
    background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4), rgba(0,0,0,0.4)), 
    url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1590309284223-3946577eb10e') center/cover fixed;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
}

.hero h1 {
    color: white;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5rem);
    backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
    padding: 15px 30px;
    border-radius: 12px;
}

/* SEÇÕES */
section {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 80px 20px;
}

h2 {
    color: var(--suica-vermelho);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    text-align: center;
}

.grid-info {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 40px;
}

.card {
    background: white;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 15px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    transition: 0.3s;
}

.card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
}

/* GALERIA */
.galeria {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
}

.galeria img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 250px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 15px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: 0.4s;
}

.galeria img:hover {
    transform: scale(1.05);
}

/* LIGHTBOX */
.lightbox {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.95);
    display: none;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
}

.lightbox img {
    max-width: 90%;
    max-height: 85%;
}

/* FOOTER */
footer {
    background: var(--suica-escuro);
    color: #bdc3c7;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 30px;
}

.highlight {
    color: var(--suica-vermelho);
    font-weight: bold;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="hero">
    <h1>Descubra a Suíça 🇨🇭</h1>
</div>

<section>
<h2>Paisagens</h2>

<div class="galeria">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1590309284223-3946577eb10e">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1501785888041-af3ef285b470">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1527668752968-14dc70a27c95">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1464822759023-fed622ff2c3b">
</div>

<p style="text-align:center; max-width:800px; margin:auto;">
A Suíça é um dos países mais bonitos do mundo, com <span class="highlight">montanhas, lagos e vilarejos</span> que parecem de filme.
</p>
</section>

<section style="background:white;">
<h2>Sobre o País</h2>

<div class="grid-info">
    <div class="card">
        <h3>💰 Economia</h3>
        <p>Uma das economias mais fortes do mundo, com destaque em bancos, tecnologia e qualidade de vida.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h3>🍫 Chocolate</h3>
        <p>O chocolate suíço é famoso mundialmente pela qualidade e sabor incomparável.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h3>🏔️ Turismo</h3>
        <p>Destino incrível para quem gosta de natureza, neve e paisagens cinematográficas.</p>
    </div>
</div>
</section>

<div class="lightbox" id="lightbox">
    <img id="lightbox-img">
</div>

<footer>
    Explorando o melhor do mundo 🚀
</footer>

<script>
const imgs = document.querySelectorAll(".galeria img");
const lightbox = document.getElementById("lightbox");
const lightboxImg = document.getElementById("lightbox-img");

imgs.forEach(img => {
    img.addEventListener("click", () => {
        lightbox.style.display = "flex";
        lightboxImg.src = img.src;
    });
});

lightbox.addEventListener("click", () => {
    lightbox.style.display = "none";
});
</script>

</body>
</html>
